<div class="modal fade" id="addPlanModal" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header"><h5 class="modal-title"><i class="bi bi-plus-circle me-2"></i>新建应急预案</h5><button class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="row g-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6"><label class="form-label">预案名称 <span class="text-danger">*</span></label><input class="form-control form-control-sm"></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><label class="form-label">预案类型</label><select class="form-select form-select-sm"><option>火灾应急</option><option>台风应急</option><option>溢油应急</option><option>人员伤亡</option><option>设备故障</option></select></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><label class="form-label">适用范围</label><input class="form-control form-control-sm" placeholder="如：全港区、装卸区"></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><label class="form-label">版本号</label><input class="form-control form-control-sm" placeholder="如：V1.0"></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><label class="form-label">编制部门</label><select class="form-select form-select-sm"><option>安全科</option><option>港务科</option><option>环保科</option><option>应急办</option><option>设备科</option></select></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><label class="form-label">有效期至</label><input type="date" class="form-control form-control-sm"></div>
                    <div class="col-12"><label class="form-label">预案说明</label><textarea class="form-control form-control-sm" rows="3" placeholder="请简要描述预案内容及启动条件..."></textarea></div>
                    <div class="col-12"><label class="form-label">上传预案文件</label><input type="file" class="form-control form-control-sm"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer"><button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" data-bs-dismiss="modal">取消</button><button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="saveForm('addPlanModal')">保 存</button></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="viewPlanModal" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header"><h5 class="modal-title"><i class="bi bi-journal-medical me-2"></i>预案详情</h5><button class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button></div>
            <div class="modal-body" style="font-size:.85rem">
                <div class="row g-2 mb-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">预案编号：</span><strong>EP-2024-001</strong></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">状态：</span><span class="badge-status status-done">已审批</span></div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">预案名称：</span>港区火灾应急处置预案</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">预案类型：</span>火灾应急</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">适用范围：</span>全港区</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">版本号：</span>V2.1</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">编制部门：</span>安全科</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">审批人：</span>港务局长</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">审批时间：</span>2024-01-15</div>
                    <div class="col-md-6"><span class="text-muted">有效期：</span>2025-12-31</div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <h6>预案主要内容</h6>
                <div class="p-3 bg-light rounded" style="font-size:.82rem">
                    <p><strong>一、适用范围：</strong>本预案适用于港区内所有区域发生火灾事故的应急处置。</p>
                    <p><strong>二、响应级别：</strong>按火灾规模分为一级（重大）、二级（较大）、三级（一般）响应。</p>
                    <p><strong>三、处置流程：</strong>发现火情→立即报警→启动应急响应→疏散人员→扑灭火灾→事后评估。</p>
                    <p><strong>四、应急队伍：</strong>消防应急队（12人）+ 港区安保队（8人）+ 医疗救护组（4人）。</p>
                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>五、演练要求：</strong>每年至少组织1次全港区综合演练，每季度组织1次专项演练。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer"><button class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" onclick="showToast('已下载')"><i class="bi bi-download me-1"></i>下载预案</button><button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" data-bs-dismiss="modal">关 闭</button></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
